The State moves to delete the enhancer of 2nd and subsequent offense.  Motion granted.
GUILTY plea entered to the amended charge of possess Heroin. Convicted.
Sentence Withheld.  Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for two (2) years.
Conditions of probation:
1) AODA assessment and follow through (if not already completed recently);
2) Submit to random urine screens and pay for same;
3) Assessment, treatment, counseling as deemed appropriate by the Departments assessment process (if not already completed recently);
4) Maintain absolute sobriety;
5) Maintain fulltime employment, schooling or combination;
6) Complete sixty (60) hours of community service;
7) Pay court costs;
8) pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.
The Court has no objection to probation being transferred to Green County.
Minutes.
